{"h00a27ac3g19d5g4230g99bcg887baa63e289": ["That - that feels good. Thank you!", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "ebaa8427-2383-8100-b647-9d17c4288400"], "h9ac4a70cg8f26g47a2g8fa2gd647f78cac96": ["Glad you're feeling better. What hurt you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "aa72f5c6-8236-9e7a-e174-814d1a5497ea"], "hb462a858g47c6g4797gb681g2f74463ec010": ["I was scouting the hills nearby. Got too close to a gnoll.", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "bb6d7dcc-3be6-edae-d982-e6b9609ff443"], "hd1a4e92cg39deg4511gaa52g54b43a8e9905": ["They're everywhere up there. Stay away if you can.", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "94eb1b83-aa53-f31d-761b-676e2e94c841"], "hdf02f75dg44e8g425fga90cg918070d429a7": ["You're welcome. Rest up.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "c4e3b402-cf19-bc2c-f6ef-d1bf1dea8389"], "h17b8e386gfe18g4b64ga20bg68d8d7af88ca": ["Yes sir!", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "196661ed-639d-cea1-4833-017b145ae391"], "hdf467d2eg9c79g497cg9313g43ca0c007108": ["Yes ma'am!", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "196661ed-639d-cea1-4833-017b145ae391"], "h89d15b24g7b6cg40f5g91fdgfc60c563308a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "71d9a4a2-2dca-017b-a910-29e4b6e8d901"], "h11beaa08g674eg4b56gb89ag8877c40ebe21": ["Please... I'm resting...", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "f7106dec-f726-a559-53e6-fbd5b028ea51"], "hb5bc83dag86b4g4bcdg9656g4dd795c96949": ["Something took a chunk out of you. What happened?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "e1391e70-4130-c8c4-cee7-cea5bef59f02"], "hf347a308g3d25g43dagab00geceb6cf14556": ["*The bird says nothing, trying to rest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "09a881d7-7713-6f35-5326-c98bcd90ad03"], "he9a65b35ga290g4539g8b7cg40515c24d50c": ["<i>Prod the bird's wing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "325d6fd6-cf18-0dfd-a7e2-019f5e570b55"], "h918976a5g5d48g4d67g9664g1a1b911a2b2a": ["Argh!", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "ef43b8ee-e2e4-a4e7-f4bc-92965aa9c379"], "h8f0f5effg67fbg44c8gb9aag62caed6816b3": ["Big dog - gnoll... I got too close...", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "72d8e5ae-8b3d-8a44-94f1-082772963aad"], "h46ec615cg5e8eg480fg9e4dg51b9e274e708": ["Where did you see these gnolls?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "517e4f44-583a-10a2-7408-b1c5c105338c"], "h3331ba5fg9048g43d7g9c2eg6a7c48ea84c7": ["Hills... near road...", "200bc56e-f3e1-445b-8b75-a5ddb541e123", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "13b674d6-967e-b058-796b-c3b774f8fc93"], "h5c343798g4cceg49c4gb0b5geea7cf09b9cb": ["*The bird lapses into silence, her head lolling to the side.* ", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "c6e0b535-343e-5f06-d5f6-32bcb406e60b"], "hb27d0b8egce32g47d2g93d6g0d8942de02f5": ["<i>Prod her again.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "d4b690fe-ce7b-788f-e92c-cbe8c39f99c7"], "h996d17d9g5da1g41a1g9e1dg30a817a263be": ["*She lies limply on the table, completely still.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "a1c25cf6-a1cb-7c2f-7a76-a21788174fce"], "h4aee005ag72aag4532gbcf0g658960d3bece": ["I'm sorry. Didn't mean to disturb you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "ba49caf9-500f-e086-e6c0-7ca0086ff523"], "h8dc3dddcg3d4fg4d6aga0afg4f64a797a40d": ["*The bird says nothing. Only the sound of its laboured breath fills the silence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "76c03dcd-2dae-6ad0-efd0-f00ad79c9945"], "h42ad874dg2944g40c4gacf9gaafb40c5b1e9": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "cb92a99f-5571-e246-2170-f28af71afeca"], "h5d65237fgea54g4481gb7fcg16680f76f6b9": ["*The bird's eyes are glassy, its breathing weak.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_WoundedBird.html", "1ca8da43-2929-181d-cba0-e978180f47ab"]}